<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Db_Adapter_Abstract::quoteTableAs is declared:</p>

<pre><code>public function quoteTableAs($ident, $alias, $auto=false)
{
    return $this-&gt;_quoteIdentifierAs($ident, $alias, $auto);
}
</code></pre>

<p>This generates a warning when $alias isn't specified. Change to:</p>

<pre><code>public function quoteTableAs($ident, $alias=null, $auto=false)
{
    return $this-&gt;_quoteIdentifierAs($ident, $alias, $auto);
}
</code></pre>

